"{\"uid\": \"rollingstone.com-product-recommendations-lifestyle-watch-paris-2024-olympics-closing-ceremony-online-free-livestream-1235077548\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"ByOscar Hartzog  If you purchase an independently reviewed product or service through a link on our website, Rolling Stone may receive an affiliate commission.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 159, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 109, \"end\": 122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rolling_Stone\", \"score\": 0.9999999867586667, \"rank\": 1.3240219187304872e-08, \"text\": \"Rolling Stone\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rolling_Stone\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rolling_Stone\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After two weeks of non-stop action, the2024 Paris Olympicsare coming to a close.\", \"from\": 161, \"to\": 241, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 205, \"end\": 210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998590283, \"rank\": 1.4102913078901194e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Sunday, the festivities wrap up with a closing ceremony, delivering some final excitement from France.\", \"from\": 242, \"to\": 347, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just like the opening ceremony, the closing ceremony has become a major draw forOlympicsviewers thanks to A-listperformancesand a grand parade of athletes.\", \"from\": 351, \"to\": 506, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The ceremony will include a symbolic handover from this year's host, Paris, to the 2028 Summer Olympics host, Los Angeles.\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 629, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 576, \"end\": 581, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998590283, \"rank\": 1.4102913078901194e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 617, \"end\": 628, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999294941542, \"rank\": 6.366907990366725e-08, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Billie Eilish, Snoop Dogg, and the Red Hot Chili Peppers are expected to perform for the event, andTom Cruisewill be pulling off aMission Impossible-style stunt.\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 791, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 645, \"end\": 655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snoop Dogg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}, {\"begin\": 665, \"end\": 686, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Hot_Chili_Peppers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Red Hot Chili Peppers\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Hot_Chili_Peppers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Hot_Chili_Peppers\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Below, we have put together a quick guide on how to watch the Olympics closing ceremony, including a way tolivestreamthe closing ceremony for free.\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 940, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris Olympics closing ceremony is airing live on NBC and streaming onPeacock.\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 1024, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 996, \"end\": 999, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.5734223614181228, \"rank\": 0.7425028929216126, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, another option for cord-cutters is to get afree trial to a live TV streaming servicethat carries NBC, such asDirecTV Stream,fubo, orHulu + Live TV.\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1181, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1131, \"end\": 1134, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.5734223614181228, \"rank\": 0.7425028929216126, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All of these cable streaming services offerfree trials- running from three to seven days - that you can use to stream the closing ceremony for free.\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1331, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just remember to cancel the trial before it ends to avoid being charged.\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1404, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you want to watch the closing ceremony on Peacock, sign up for asubscription herefor $7.99 a month (Peacock does not offer a free trial, unfortunately).\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1560, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1450, \"end\": 1457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.7446044623786183, \"rank\": 0.3429949057748967, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No matter which option you choose, you will be able to watch the closing ceremony online from home.\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1661, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Plus, all of these options will offer livestreams of Olympic events scheduled to take place on Sunday before the ceremony, including women's basketball, cycling, volleyball, and wrestling.\", \"from\": 1662, \"to\": 1850, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2024 Olympics closing ceremony is happening on Sunday, Aug. 11.\", \"from\": 1852, \"to\": 1919, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The ceremony starts at 2 p.m. ET/11 a.m. PT for US viewers.\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 1979, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1968, \"end\": 1970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.8770969268427494, \"rank\": 0.1393554743495595, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year's Olympics closing ceremony will feature live broadcasts from both Paris and Los Angeles, as well as prerecorded segments.\", \"from\": 1981, \"to\": 2113, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2058, \"end\": 2063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998590283, \"rank\": 1.4102913078901194e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2068, \"end\": 2079, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999294941542, \"rank\": 6.366907990366725e-08, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NBC's coverage will be hosted by Jimmy Fallon and Mike Tirico with supporting commentary from Olympians Johnny Weir and Tara Lipinski.\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2248, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2114, \"end\": 2117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.5734223614181228, \"rank\": 0.7425028929216126, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}, {\"begin\": 2147, \"end\": 2159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Fallon\", \"score\": 0.9800161037782861, \"rank\": 0.020391395758253248, \"text\": \"Jimmy Fallon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Fallon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Fallon\"}, {\"begin\": 2164, \"end\": 2175, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Tirico\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mike Tirico\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Tirico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Tirico\"}, {\"begin\": 2218, \"end\": 2229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johnny_Weir\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Johnny Weir\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13219587\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johnny_Weir\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johnny_Weir\"}, {\"begin\": 2234, \"end\": 2247, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tara_Lipinski\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tara Lipinski\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13219587\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tara_Lipinski\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tara_Lipinski\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just like the opening ceremony, there will also be some performances from major acts including Billie Eilish, Snoop Dogg, and the Red Hot Chili Peppers, according toreports.\", \"from\": 2250, \"to\": 2423, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2360, \"end\": 2370, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snoop Dogg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}, {\"begin\": 2380, \"end\": 2401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Hot_Chili_Peppers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Red Hot Chili Peppers\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Hot_Chili_Peppers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Hot_Chili_Peppers\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The performances will be a mix of live broadcasts and pre-recorded content, all from Los Angeles.\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2521, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2509, \"end\": 2520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999294941542, \"rank\": 6.366907990366725e-08, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the most highly-anticipated segments of the closing ceremony is a flag-transfer by Tom Cruise.\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2624, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2613, \"end\": 2623, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheMission Impossiblestar willreportedlyrepeal down the Stade de France on live TV, before the broadcast cuts to a prerecorded clip of the movie star skydiving down the Hollywood sign in Los Angeles.\", \"from\": 2625, \"to\": 2824, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2794, \"end\": 2808, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hollywood sign\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\"}, {\"begin\": 2812, \"end\": 2823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999294941542, \"rank\": 6.366907990366725e-08, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We want to hear it.\", \"from\": 2826, \"to\": 2845, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Send us a tip using our anonymous form.\", \"from\": 2846, \"to\": 2885, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rolling Stone is a part of Penske Media Corporation.\", \"from\": 2887, \"to\": 2939, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2887, \"end\": 2900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rolling_Stone\", \"score\": 0.9999999867586667, \"rank\": 1.3240219187304872e-08, \"text\": \"Rolling Stone\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rolling_Stone\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rolling_Stone\"}, {\"begin\": 2914, \"end\": 2926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penske_Media_Corporation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Penske Media\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penske_Media_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penske_Media_Corporation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 2026 Rolling Stone, LLC.\", \"from\": 2940, \"to\": 2966, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2962, \"end\": 2965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\", \"score\": 0.9999999883050351, \"rank\": 1.1597581474292351e-08, \"text\": \"LLC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 2967, \"to\": 2987, \"entities\": []}]}"